I started playing shortly after the release of Kunark(3 days or so to be exact).  Just to prove myself wrong I went to all the places that annoyed me back then to see if they still had the same bugs.  Guess what, the bugs are still there.  Mobs still run underground in FoB, Guards still con incorrectly in the Karana's.  Ogres still con amiable when they attack on sight, Falls for 10k damage still happen while zoning.  Zoning with low hp's still causes all your buffs to go away.  CS still takes an hour + to say they can't help you, and the Lead GM will be notified.  The advertised features of SoL still arn't there.  Luclin is still super laggy with a 64meg AMD GeForce 3 video card on a Athlon Palamino 1600+ based board  with 512meg DDRAM.  Add that to my countries currency being worth only slightly more then the Mexican Peso(Canada), and suddenly VI can take this game and shove it.  Paying $Cdn15.00 to be a beta tester was bad enough, but this goes to far for me.  I guess the only question left is do I E-Bay my toons or do I just delete them, and forget all the time I spent on them.  Poor Sony.  I guess being a multi-national conglomerate they can't afford to do things right.<P>--------------------<P>Tanelsa Teir'dal Necro 41(semi-retired)<BR>Illessa Scaled Shaman 58<BR>Dhast The Discerning Ogress Barsher<BR>CT the place to be
