d with accounts closed etc, they are probably at about 250,000 to 300,000 paying subscribers, if that.  Still a high number, but it will bring your figures down a notch.<P>It's really amazing to see people that have no clue what goes into business, gaming or MMORPGs sit here and argue points that can't have any knowledge of without being part of at least one of those items.  Being only a consumer makes people ignorant of the situation and being ignorant of the situation means you won't know the facts.  Leave the game if you don't like the price increase, but don't try to tell Verant you know what they are doing when you have no clue what it takes to do what they do.<P>Oh, one more thing, I am not an employee of Sony, Verant, 989, etc....etc....etc....
